    Scope and Contents
FIRST CONGREGATIONAL CHURCH
Dr. Virgil Myers, minister, recalls life in Ohio and the move to Springfield to minister the First Congregational Church: early farm life, college education in Ohio, the First Congregational Church in Marietta, WWII, the move to Springfield, fire of 1956, assistance from Temple B'rith Sholom, rebuilding the church, his ministry, and the church's centennial celebration.3 tapes, 210 mins., 57 pp.
Interview by Constance Bostick, 1975
OPEN
See collateral file: photos and articles about the fire and the church.  
  
